data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is a true gem nestled in a vibrant and highly sought-after neighborhood. From its prime location to its cozy interiors, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in Lancaster City.  Be ready to enjoy shopping, restaurants, parks, and more just moments away from home, making this an ideal choice for those who crave the urban lifestyle.  Cute as a button, spacious, updated on the inside, and ready for new owners to call it home!  Don't miss your chance to see 22 E Liberty Street!  Call today to schedule your private showing.
